<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>{% include "court_base.css" %}</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-block">
        <strong>Date:</strong> {{ date_of_draft }}<br><br>
        <strong>To,</strong><br>
        The Manager / Director,<br>
        {{ shelter_name }}<br>
        {{ shelter_address }}
    </div>

    <div class="subject-line">
        SUBJECT: Referral for Emergency Shelter Accommodation
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        Dear Sir/Madam,
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        This letter is to refer <strong>{{ applicant_name }}</strong> for emergency shelter accommodation at your establishment. The individual is currently in a crisis situation and requires immediate safe housing.
    </div>

    <h2>Referred Person Details</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Name</th><td>{{ applicant_name }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Age</th><td>{{ applicant_age | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Contact</th><td>{{ applicant_phone | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Crisis Category</th><td>{{ crisis_category | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Urgency Level</th><td>{{ urgency_level | default("High") }}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Background</h2>
    <div class="body-text">
        {{ draft_body_summary }}
    </div>

    <h2>Immediate Needs</h2>
    <div class="body-text">
        {% if needs_list %}
        <ul>
            {% for need in needs_list %}
            <li>{{ need }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% else %}
        Safe accommodation, food, and access to essential services.
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        Your immediate attention and assistance in providing shelter to the referred person would be greatly appreciated.
    </div>

    <div class="signature-block">
        <div class="line"></div>
        <strong>Sahayak — Last Mile Justice Navigator</strong><br>
        Automated Referral System<br>
        Date: {{ date_of_draft }}
    </div>

    <div id="page-footer" style="text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; color: #666;">
        Page <pdf:pagenumber> of <pdf:pagecount>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
